  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d33b84adc37945cb8aa0bfd653e09e1, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d33b84adc37945cb8aa0bfd653e09e1, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d33b84adc37945cb8aa0bfd653e09e1, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d33b84adc37945cb8aa0bfd653e09e1, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6631694f571404520adcedcfd521e0de, type: 3}
  image1Texts:
  - Text 1.1
  image2Texts:
  - 'Rising temperatures bring more than discomfort. '
  - Toxic air pollution and heavy pollen have already taken the lives of countless
    cats and dogs...
  image3Texts:
  - Silently overwhelming their small lungs and leaving human connection more fragile
    than ever before.
  image4Texts:
  - Tedbot, a leader in the robotic animal space, unveiled their fully-autonomous
    and hyper-realistic dog at the 2040 Scalable Labs & Open Products Conference.
  - 'Tedbot CEO came up with the idea for Bork based on his personal experience,
    losing his former pet to climate change. '
  image5Texts:
  - Motivated by this gap, CEO set out to develop a robotic dog that could offer
    the same companionship without the risks.
  image6Texts:
  - Thanks to cutting-edge technology, Bork looks, feels, and interacts just like
    a real puppy.
  image7Texts:
  - They have realistic, soft fur and head movements that mimic a real dog.
  - Embedded touch sensors react to human touch  and intensity, producing dog reactions...
  - Including authentic sounds recorded from ViewTube doggy complications.
  image8Texts:
  - Despite their realistic appearance and behaviour, caring for a companion is much
    simpler than ever before.
  - Firstly, Bork is a self-cleaning companion, who brings convenience to everyday
    life, thanks to their smart capacities.
  image9Texts:
  - "They provide peace of mind by sending video updates to users' devices when they\u2019re
    away from home."
  - "They also play music and answers phone calls \u2013 even helping with summarization
    and creative writing... "
  - Bork makes life at home more productive and enjoyable.
  image10Texts:
  - "Bork will be a man\u2019s best friend forever."
  - 'They are the first companion ever known to be able to age and reverse its aging
    process. '
  image11Texts:
  - 'At the right time, they collapse into a blob of tissue and reverts back into
    its juvenile puppy stage, becoming young all over again. '
  image12Texts:
  - "By embedding ethical and safety rules into the very core of its AI, Bork is
    not only smart\u2014he\u2019s trustworthy."
  - Their benefits can extend to a wide range of people. Bork can bring joy and emotional
    support to residents who feel isolated.
  - Bork provides a non-judgmental companion that helps reduce anxiety and stress.
  image13Texts:
  - 'According to the developers, Bork systems continuously monitor its environment,
    assess risk, and prioritize human well-being over any programmed task. '
  image14Texts:
  - "This means that whether it\u2019s assisting an elderly person with mobility
    or helping children with homework... "
  image15Texts:
  - Bork operates under a safety-first philosophy.
  - 'Bork is the future of companionship and he is here to stay. '
  image16Texts:
  - ACCELETATOR
  image17Texts:
  - identity verification log...
  image18Texts:
  - "interaction rhythm: analyzed\u2026 task method: categorized\u2026 error pattern:
    documented\u2026 "
  - "response timing: measured\u2026 movement: catalogued\u2026 "
  - 'CONFIDENCE MATCH: 34.2%'
  - 'STATUS: verification failed.'
  - 'ESCALATION: flagged for posthuman audit.'
  - ...
  image19Texts:
  - "It doesn\u2019t think you, or anyone in this area belongs here. "
  - "You are one of the few \u201Canomalies\u201D who hasn't gone missing yet."
  - Leave this town IMMEDIATELY before it finds you.
